{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/s__4_.png?t=1736215323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Maelstr\u00f6m Legacy: The Tesla Mystery</i> is a point-and-click puzzle adventure game for PC and Mac. Set in an anachronistic Paris, you lead the investigation when Nikola Tesla, President of the High Scientific Council and organizer of the Scientific Congress, mysteriously vanishes! Dive into an Art Nouveau and steampunk-inspired world, where vibrant characters and endless challenges await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/s__5_.png?t=1736215323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hayao Maelstr\u00f6m, a young Japanese scientist and inventor, arrived in France two years ago and now resides in the quaint village of Valfutaie in Haute-Savoie. One day, he receives an official letter signed by Tesla himself, inviting him to the decennial Scientific Congress in Paris, held at the Eiffel Tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, just as Tesla concludes his opening speech, the lights suddenly go out. When they return, Tesla has disappeared without a trace!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While the police launch their investigation, Hayao and his loyal dog, Alpina, set out to uncover the truth behind Tesla's disappearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Hayao and Alpina, you\u2019ll encounter an eclectic cast of intriguing characters\u2014and perhaps make a few enemies along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/7.png?t=1736215323\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/s__6_.png?t=1736215323\" /><strong>Investigate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with elements in the environment to uncover valuable clues and information.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/tesla1.gif?t=1736215323\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the solutions to intricate puzzles that block your path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/tesla2.gif?t=1736215323\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Logic Battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some characters may try to hide the truth... You\u2019ll have to overcome their \u201cLogic Shields\u201d to reveal it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/tesla3.gif?t=1736215323\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736215323","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/page.bg.jpg?t=1736215323","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736215323","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736215323","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016820/extras/s__4_.png?t=1736215323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Maelstr\u00f6m Legacy: The Tesla Mystery</i> is a point-and-click puzzle adventure game for PC and Mac. Set in an anachronistic Paris, you lead the investigation when Nikola Tesla, President of the High Scientific Council and organ